vimrc i'm using, enjoy~~


HOW TO INSTALL
(1) cp vimrc ~/.vim_runtime
(2) cd ~/.vim_runtime append __vimrc to your ~/.vimrc
(3) run install.sh 

this work is based on http://amix.dk/blog/post/19486#The-ultimate-vim-configuration-vimrc

add functions:

(1) ctrl + right arrow or ctrl + left arrow to switch files in the buffuer
如果你用的是SecureCRT，那么需要用Mapkey来使用这两个功能：
    * emulate as xterm
    * map key ctrl + left arrow == \033[1;5C    ctrl + right arrow == \033[1;5D
 
(2) add matchit.vim plugin, which is useful in html/xml edit for fast location tag

(3) add go lang support

(4) (testing)add plugin ctrlp, how to use : https://github.com/kien/ctrlp.vim
    default add Ctrl+p as shortcut to invoke ctrlp plugin

